不会不太好<br /><br />PS：跟楼主的家庭地位无关","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/903503","replies":54,"created_ts":1671434799,"created":"15:26:39","title":"怎么办，媳妇买的口罩标准不是医用外科口罩级别的，我要不要提醒一下，感觉不太好","author":"xuromky","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xuromky","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a2ae/ee87/264680_mini.png?m=1652527125"},{"id":903400,"node":"分享创造","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/create","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1660301119","description":"<h2>概览</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>🤟 有喜欢南京市民李先生的吗？  </li>\n<li>🐝 周末时间和 Turkyden 结合 Pake 给搞了一个「 LiZhi 」客户端给喜欢 B 哥的朋友，支持 Mac/Winows/Linux 多系统，很小大概 3M 左右，几乎包括的 B 哥所有的专辑和演出歌曲，还有 4 个很值得一看的演唱会。</li>\n<li>🎉 代码实现来自 Turkyden ，资源用 GoldSubmarine 的 nj-lizhi ，我来打杂和提需求，可去 Pake 下载。 </li>\n</ul>\n<h3><a href=\"https://github.com/tw93/Pake\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/tw93/Pake</a></h3>\n<h2>效果</h2>\n<p><strong>首页</strong>：\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://cdn.fliggy.com/upic/vIeQuZ.png\"/></p>\n<p><strong>专辑页</strong>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://cdn.fliggy.com/upic/TFyB7o.png\"/></p>\n<p><strong>演出页</strong>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://cdn.fliggy.com/upic/wteeEA.png\"/></p>\n<h2>版权说明</h2>\n<p>关于版权，我们在源项目<a href=\"https://github.com/turkyden/lizhi#%E7%89%88%E6%9D%83%E5%A3%B0%E6%98%8E\" rel=\"nofollow\">底部</a>有加一个还算正式的申明。\n版权全部归于李志所有，我们仅从互联网搜集资源进行合并整理。从李志公众号发布的声明来看，他也希望会得到传播，所以才贸然建立了此 Repository ，并已发送邮件告知李志。若邮件回复不允许，会立即删除。</p>\n<h2>关于 Pake</h2>\n<p>Pake 比较特别的是，相比传统的 Electron 套壳打包，大小要小将近 40 倍，一般 2M 左右，此外由于底层使用的，Rust Tauri 框架，性能体验较 JS 框架要轻快不少，内存小很多；此外实现了通用快捷键的透传、容器通信、样式改写注入、沉浸式的窗口、拖动、简化使用流程优化等功能，有一点点可玩性，你可以自己直接打包喜欢的。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/903400","replies":53,"created_ts":1671411790,"created":"09:03:10","title":"🤖 做了一个精致的李志音乐桌面 App","author":"tw93","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/tw93","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/164c/eb62/109043_mini.png?m=1665799887"},{"id":903541,"node":"随想","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/random","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/093f/65e0/59_mini.png?m=1615956453","description":"以前听谁说的，只要每个人都把口罩带严严实实，能阻隔 95%以上的病毒传播率。<br /><br />问题是大部分人都做到了啊。马路上没带口罩，都是极少数人。<br /><br />可这波病毒感觉都能无视口罩，真的是非常莫名。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/903541","replies":51,"created_ts":1671441906,"created":"17:25:06","title":"这波毒株是会魔法攻击吗？光靠物理防御完全无效啊。","author":"tool2d","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/tool2d","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9e4b/c61b/561400_mini.png?m=1667209262"},{"id":903442,"node":"分享发现","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1650127281","description":"<p>微信键盘发布了，但是千万别下载使用，因为会非常卡，商店划不动的那种</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/903442","replies":50,"created_ts":1671419601,"created":"11:13:21","title":"微信键盘发布了，但是千万别用","author":"datongkaze","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/datongkaze","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a0bf/7b36/214518_mini.png?m=1587368317"},{"id":903486,"node":"Android","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/android","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1651385965","description":"<p>已知:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>华为官方不提供解锁 BL 工具。</li>\n<li>有稳定的梯子，用原生不会困难。</li>\n<li>芯片为 麒麟 980 。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>问:</p>\n<pre><code>1. 有没有比较成熟稳定的刷机工具（解锁 BL ）。\n2. 推荐几个国内外的安卓论坛。\n</code></pre>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/903486","replies":41,"created_ts":1671431218,"created":"14:26:58","title":"关于华为 P30 解锁 BL 并刷原生安卓。","author":"mmr","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/mmr","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e3c9/244b/588157_mini.png?m=1657934993"},{"id":903398,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"1 、前段时间 80 块钱 20 